topic.title: Discharge Medication - conformance rules

section.p: The Discharge Medications entry codes medications that the patient is intended to take (or stop) after discharge.

ol.li:
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] templateId ( CONF:16760, CONF:16761 ) such that it
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @root="2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.4.35"
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="ACT" Act (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.6 HL7ActClass) (CONF:7689, R2.0=CONF:1098-7689)
